<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>七律 on Script Adults</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/tags/%E4%B8%83%E5%BE%8B/</link><description>Recent content in 七律 on Script Adults</description><image><title>Script Adults</title><url>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/images/papermod-cover.png</url><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/images/papermod-cover.png</link></image><generator>Hugo -- 0.140.0</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 02:54:44 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://katsuragicsl.github.io/tags/%E4%B8%83%E5%BE%8B/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>自樂</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%87%AA%E6%A8%82/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 02:54:44 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%87%AA%E6%A8%82/</guid><description>&lt;p>懶理職場獻媚密，歸來自聽雨連珠。&lt;br>
凡生笑我無心眼，漆吏知吾乃樂魚。&lt;br>
孔聖隨心不踰矩，詩痴久諷律無虞。&lt;br>
唯耽無益雕蟲技，最是優悠意氣舒。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>憶中大</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%86%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 03:01:02 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%86%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7/</guid><description>&lt;p>夢入當年新亞宿，涼乘合一水旁陰。&lt;br>
青山一別書香薄，石壁空鐫名姓深。&lt;br>
錯把孤居作勤學，徒懷熱鬧論經音。&lt;br>
盈頭鬒髮今朝落，默撫長鬚復擁衾。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>詠巴西柔術</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A9%A0%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E6%9F%94%E8%A1%93/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 03:00:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A9%A0%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E6%9F%94%E8%A1%93/</guid><description>&lt;p>褒衣博帶非儒服，肉搏毫釐不動刀。&lt;br>
灑汗披襟相浹背，騎胸抱頸若分桃。&lt;br>
難如對奕能開智，巧使剛柔解六韜。&lt;br>
此藝修心養吾性，藏鋒斂戾伏波濤。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>大涌橋路</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%A4%A7%E6%B6%8C%E6%A9%8B%E8%B7%AF/</link><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 15:06:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%A4%A7%E6%B6%8C%E6%A9%8B%E8%B7%AF/</guid><description>&lt;p>向晚歸車涌上過，遺田古早有牛鞅。 &lt;br>
朝擠港島珠纓路，夜食沙田布袋糧。 &lt;br>
幾覆瀝青橋主易，唯留兩岸水湄長。 &lt;br>
幽村狗喚誰家鬼，一叫三迴促斷腸。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>閱杜甫生平</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%96%B1%E6%9D%9C%E7%94%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%B9%B3/</link><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 15:05:24 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E9%96%B1%E6%9D%9C%E7%94%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%B9%B3/</guid><description>&lt;p>嘗題蜀相三分國，又寄宮垣想玉珂。&lt;br>
久憶洛都疲慧眼，心傷楚地殞冬河。&lt;br>
憂民睿敏蟬聯出，不變江山又幾多。&lt;br>
宋滅元亡明復繼，何需俊傑枉蹉跎。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>望華街</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9C%9B%E8%8F%AF%E8%A1%97/</link><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 15:04:17 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9C%9B%E8%8F%AF%E8%A1%97/</guid><description>&lt;p>日出華街盈客旅，深宵穢巷舞蠅蚊。&lt;br>
光陰不惜花齡女，玉手磨成半片皸。&lt;br>
昨夢金貂英氣煥，明朝滿鏡老眉矄。&lt;br>
三坪礎剷千年樹，百載勞來兩尺墳。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>古不賤今</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%8F%A4%E4%B8%8D%E8%B3%A4%E4%BB%8A/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 01:56:13 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E5%8F%A4%E4%B8%8D%E8%B3%A4%E4%BB%8A/</guid><description>&lt;p>人常詠古歌仁聖，似是今人鄙不勝。&lt;br>
叔夜孤高難仿效，夷齊朽滯若瘕癥。&lt;br>
西山槁槁饑薇蕨，一曲淒淒絕廣陵。&lt;br>
史內千秋寸心辨，賢愚莫有固規繩。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>見族人炫祖上之富</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A6%8B%E6%97%8F%E4%BA%BA%E7%82%AB%E7%A5%96%E4%B8%8A%E4%B9%8B%E5%AF%8C/</link><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 01:35:25 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E8%A6%8B%E6%97%8F%E4%BA%BA%E7%82%AB%E7%A5%96%E4%B8%8A%E4%B9%8B%E5%AF%8C/</guid><description>&lt;p>誰家三水田千里，舊榭新軒盡姓陳。&lt;br>
輒耀膏粱矜祖富，詩書少讀曝詞貧。&lt;br>
詢其祖業餘多少，賞彼紅腮半怯嗔。&lt;br>
渴鬼愁看舊時屋，年年祭饗供他人。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>無題</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%84%A1%E9%A1%8C/</link><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 22:33:12 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E7%84%A1%E9%A1%8C/</guid><description>&lt;p>陳衣欲搗子規啼，嗽穿重簾夜更淒。&lt;br>
十載茅齋茂陵臥，雙行枯淚太常妻。&lt;br>
清心昔捨青雲路，俗務今催洗耳溪。&lt;br>
半世徒勞芳自賞，來生捨筆執鋤犁。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>李恥杜愁</title><link>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9D%8E%E6%81%A5%E6%9D%9C%E6%84%81/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:01:14 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://katsuragicsl.github.io/blogs/%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%9E/%E6%9D%8E%E6%81%A5%E6%9D%9C%E6%84%81/</guid><description>&lt;p>性俗全無墨在胸，冥搜拙句砌機峰。&lt;br>
詩成引得謫仙恥，筆落愁催工部容。&lt;br>
既與深情詩韻繫，何教秉賦櫟樗庸。&lt;br>
如吾堪作違心事，簡朽帛殘枯筆封。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>